Package org.zone.region.group

Interface Group

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<Group>, Identifiable
All Known Implementing Classes:
SimpleGroup
public interface Group extends Identifiable, Comparable<Group>
A group of players found within a zone. Think of this like a Permissions group only specifically for a zone. A group can have GroupKeys which act like permissions for that group within the zone.
